data.description: Nestled in the heart of Hillsboro, this Craftsman-style home with 2 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a spacious loft, it offers the perfect blend of contemporary living and modern charm. As you step inside, you're greeted by an open concept main floor. The living area seamlessly flows into the dining space and the kitchen, creating a space perfect for gatherings and entertaining. Thoughtfully designed kitchen, where you'll find stainless steel appliances and an island with ample seating, making it a welcoming hub for family and friends. Venture upstairs to discover two spacious bedrooms, each offering a tranquil sanctuary for rest and relaxation. The primary suite is a haven in itself, boasting a generous walk-in closet and a full bath that is a true retreat. This ensuite bath features a luxurious soaking tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day, and a separate walk-in shower. For those who need a versatile space, the large loft area awaits your creative touch. Whether you envision it as a home office, a cozy reading nook, or a playroom for children, the possibilities are endless. Close proximity to shopping, dining, and easy access to public transportation. Hillsboro's charming community and vibrant city life are at your doorstep! [Home Energy Score = 8. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10223727]
